   "source": [
    "# 12.3 记忆 (Memory)\n",
    "\n",
    "记忆系统使Agent能在交互过程中保持和利用历史信息。\n",
    "\n",
    "本节涵盖：短期记忆、长期记忆、工作记忆"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. 短期记忆与长期记忆\n",
    "\n",
    "**短期记忆**：当前对话的上下文窗口，存储最近的交互历史，受限于模型的上下文长度。\n",
    "\n",
    "**长期记忆**：跨会话持久化存储的信息，通常使用向量数据库实现语义检索。\n",
    "\n",
    "**核心区别**：\n",
    "- 短期：对话内，自动维护，有长度限制\n",
    "- 长期：跨对话，需要显式存储和检索，容量大"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import torch\n",
    "import torch.nn as nn\n",
    "import torch.nn.functional as F\n",
    "\n",
    "torch.manual_seed(42)\n",
    "\n",
    "class VectorMemory(nn.Module):\n",
    "    def __init__(self, d=64, capacity=100):\n",
    "        super().__init__()\n",
    "        self.d = d\n",
    "        self.capacity = capacity\n",
    "        self.encoder = nn.Linear(d, 32)\n",
    "        self.register_buffer('keys', torch.zeros(capacity, 32))\n",
    "        self.register_buffer('values', torch.zeros(capacity, d))\n",
    "        self.size = 0\n",
    "\n",
    "    def store(self, key, value):\n",
    "        idx = self.size % self.capacity\n",
    "        self.keys[idx] = F.normalize(self.encoder(key), dim=-1).detach()\n",
    "        self.values[idx] = value.detach()\n",
    "        self.size += 1\n",
    "\n",
    "    def retrieve(self, query, top_k=3):\n",
    "        q = F.normalize(self.encoder(query), dim=-1)\n",
    "        n_stored = min(self.size, self.capacity)\n",
    "        scores = q @ self.keys[:n_stored].T\n",
    "        top_indices = scores.topk(min(top_k, n_stored)).indices\n",
    "        return self.values[top_indices], scores[top_indices]\n",
    "\n",
    "memory = VectorMemory()\n",
    "for i in range(10):\n",
    "    key = torch.randn(1, 64)\n",
    "    value = torch.randn(1, 64) + i * 0.1\n",
    "    memory.store(key, value)\n",
    "\n",
    "query = torch.randn(1, 64)\n",
    "retrieved, scores = memory.retrieve(query, top_k=3)\n",
    "\n",
    "print('=== Long-Term Memory (Vector Store) ===')\n",
    "print(f'Stored memories: {memory.size}')\n",
    f"print(f'Query: {query.shape}')\n",
    "print(f'Retrieved top-3 scores: {scores[0].detach().tolist()}')\n",
    "print(f'Retrieved values shape: {retrieved.shape}')\n",
    "print(f'\\nKey: Vector memory enables semantic retrieval of past experiences.')\n",
    "print(f'Agent can recall relevant information from thousands of past interactions.')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. 工作记忆 (Working Memory)\n",
    "\n",
    "**目的**：为当前任务维护临时工作空间\n",
    "\n",
    "**基本原理**：类似人类的\"草稿纸\"，Agent在推理过程中可以读写工作记忆，存储中间结果、推理步骤等。\n",
    "\n",
    "**与短期/长期记忆的区别**：\n",
    "- 短期记忆：对话历史（只读）\n",
    "- 长期记忆：持久化知识（检索式）\n",
    "- 工作记忆：当前任务的临时空间（读写）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import torch\n",
    "import torch.nn as nn\n",
    "\n",
    "torch.manual_seed(42)\n",
    "\n",
    "class WorkingMemory:\n",
    "    def __init__(self, d=64, max_slots=8):\n",
    "        self.d = d\n",
    "        self.max_slots = max_slots\n",
    "        self.slots = {}\n",
    "\n",
    "    def write(self, key, value_tensor):\n",
    "        if len(self.slots) >= self.max_slots:\n",
    "            oldest = list(self.slots.keys())[0]\n",
    "            del self.slots[oldest]\n",
    "        self.slots[key] = value_tensor.detach().clone()\n",
    "\n",
    "    def read(self, key):\n",
    "        return self.slots.get(key, torch.zeros(1, self.d))\n",
    "\n",
    "    def list_keys(self):\n",
    "        return list(self.slots.keys())\n",
    "\n",
    "wm = WorkingMemory(d=64, max_slots=5)\n",
    "\n",
    "print('=== Working Memory (Scratchpad) ===')\n",
    "for i in range(7):\n",
    "    key = f'step_{i}_result'\n",
    "    value = torch.randn(1, 64) * (i + 1)\n",
    "    wm.write(key, value)\n",
    "    print(f'Write: {key} (slots used: {len(wm.slots)}/{wm.max_slots})')\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f'\\nCurrent keys in working memory: {wm.list_keys()}')\n",
    "result = wm.read('step_5_result')\n",
    "print(f'Read step_5_result: norm={result.norm():.4f}')\n",
    "print(f'\\nKey: Working memory is a read-write scratchpad for current task.')\n",
    "print(f'Older entries are evicted when capacity is reached.')"
   ]
  }
